%81%EC%96%B4/change\" title=\"changes\">changes</a> that cannot be <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/controlled\" title=\"controlled\">controlled</a> and can <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/influence\" title=\"influence\">influence</a> a <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/situation\" title=\"situation\">situation</a></li>\n<li>bikering : <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/argument\" title=\"arguments\">arguments</a> about things that are not <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/important\" title=\"important\">important</a></li>\n<li>circumvent : to <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/avoid\" title=\"avoid\">avoid</a> something, <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/especially\" title=\"especially\">especially</a> <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/clever\" title=\"cleverly\">cleverly</a> or <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/illegally\" title=\"illegally\">illegally</a></li>\n<li>coincidental : <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/happening\" title=\"happening\">happening</a> by <a href=\"https://dictionary.cambridge.org/ko/%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%84/%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4/coincidence\" title=\"coincidence\">coincidence</a>(동시에 발생하는)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2024-03-13\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2024-03-13\" aria-label=\"2024 03 13 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3